Constructor Detail

WPIImage

public WPIImage(java.awt.image.BufferedImage image)
Instantiates a WPIImage from a BufferedImage. Useful for interacting with swing. This will not keep a reference to the given image, so any modification to this WPIImage will not change the given image.

Parameters:
image - the image to copy into a WPIImage

WPIImage

public WPIImage(com.googlecode.javacv.cpp.opencv_core.IplImage image)
Instantiates a WPIImage from the given opencv_core.IplImage. The resulting image will be directly wrapped around the given image, and so any modifications to the WPIImage will reflect on the given image.

Parameters:
image - the image to wrap
